latestPosts.caption:
“The wedding 11/10/2022”🤍🧿
Last but not least, I would like to thank each and every single person who actually showed their love and support for my henna and wedding contents that I have been sharing so far, it truly means a lot. Thank you so much guys 🫶🏼

“Our wedding took place on 11th of October 2022 in one of the most beautiful historical castles (Tjolöholm Castle) in Sweden.🤍
As much as I wanted the Henna ceremony to be true to the Afghan traditions as possible, it was something the other way when it came to choosing the venue for our wedding. Me and my husband wanted somewhere that paid tribute to our journey together. So it came down to choosing this beautiful historical castle, Tjholom Castle, located in south of Gothenburg, Sweden.
The castle was built between 1898-1904 and it has been Sweden’s leading arts and craft property. 
Its unique architecture, beautiful gardens and the south facing views of the sea provide an ideal location for a fairytale wedding.”🤍🧿

latestPosts.caption:
شب حنا ٠٨/١٠/٢٠٢٢
To sum up, when it comes to celebrations, we (Afghans) have got some of the best traditional outfits, music, and cuisine. I have never felt pressured to include other cultural influences and I believe I kept everything true to our ethnical standards. Most importantly, everything went exactly as I always imagined and dreamed of celebrating my henna.♥️🇦🇫🧿
Eid Mubarak 🩵🧿
